0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(OVERVIEW) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(This guide helps frontline support and line leads diagnose label print drift, skew, and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(horizontal offset on the fictional PRN-410 thermal label printer used at packing lanes. It) Tj
0 -14 Td
(assumes the printer powers on and feeds media, but the printed image does not align) Tj
0 -14 Td
(consistently with the label stock.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(COMMON SYMPTOMS) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Printed barcodes drift toward the leading or trailing edge after several labels.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- The first label after calibration looks correct, but the next ten labels walk out of) Tj
0 -14 Td
(position.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Left margin is acceptable on narrow labels but clipped on wide labels loaded from the same) Tj
0 -14 Td
(roll family.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Operators report frequent media-out or gap-sensor prompts after roll changes.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(LIKELY CAUSES) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Improper media sensor position after a roll change.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Print-head pressure imbalance or partially latched print-head assembly.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Incorrect label size, gap, or top-of-form setting in the workstation profile.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Contamination on the platen roller causing the stock to drift under tension.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(DIAGNOSTIC WORKFLOW) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Confirm the exact label part number and compare it with the workstation profile currently) Tj
0 -14 Td
(assigned to the lane.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Inspect media path alignment marks and verify the movable guide lightly touches the stock) Tj
0 -14 Td
(without bowing it.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Clean the platen roller and sensor window, then print five blank feeds followed by a) Tj
0 -14 Td
(calibration page.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Print a ten-label test batch and note whether drift begins immediately or only after the) Tj
0 -14 Td
(printer warms up.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- If the issue appears only on one workstation, compare page setup and printer preference) Tj
0 -14 Td
(values with a known-good lane using the same label size.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
ET
endstream
